name: Lucky lady horseshoe necklace
description:
Maybe you or a friend need a little extra luck? Maybe you're already so lucky your friends call you Vegas? Maybe you have super fond memories of your first childhood pony ride? Whatever the case may be, this necklace is awesome. Delicate, feminine and best of all, super lucky!

One for you and one for your bestie.

A delicately hammered horseshoe centered on 16" of diamond cut chain. 2.25" extender with sparkly gemstone.

name: Jenna delicate stacking chain ring
description:
Feminine and delicate with just the right punch, the Jenna chain ring is great for stacking, wearing alone and especially for gifting to a friend. The 20 gauge band is lightly hammer textured and centered with beautiful rolo chain in the opposing metal.

Don't see your size on the list of options? Just send a message with your order and we'll be happy to make it in whatever size you need!

name: Devorah triple crystal necklace
description:
Get mystical!

Three chunky quartz crystals floating on a 27" of diamond cut chain. 

Easy to wear, great for layering and another great way to mix your metals.

And if that's not enough, 25% of all proceeds from this necklace are donated to Woman, Inc.

Since 1978, W.O.M.A.N, Inc. (Women Organized to Make Abuse Non-Existent) has offered a wide range of holistic services, supporting survivors of domestic violence.  
http://womaninc.org

name: Lydia chandelier hoops
description:
Lydia is a free spirit, a bohemian princess, an all around adventurer - and quite frankly, she's gorgeous. She's got it all covered and now you will too. 

Now you'll never need to make that very difficult decision between hoops or chandeliers. And our favorite, the 14k gold fill and sterling combo. Boom!

At their longest, they hang 2.75" and are 1.25" wide. They are lightweight and have fantastic movement.

options.name: 14k gold fill with sterling accents- lime chalcedony
14k gold fill with sterling accents- hot pink jade
14k gold fill with sterling accents - rutilated quartz

name: Penny mini hoop earring
description:
At just over 1" long and 3/4" wide, the Penny mini is a fantastic lightweight, easy breezy, everyday hoop. An expertly wrapped gemstone adds the perfect pop of pizzaz. 

These are the poster child for the "one for you, one for me" style of shopping we love so much...

name: Vanessa 5 chain bracelet
description:
Simple elegance is sexy and so is this bracelet. 5 strands of alternating 14k gold fill (and/or) sterling silver chain in all different styles, shapes and textures. Finish each end with rough cut garnets and a citrine drop that hangs seductively off the wrist and you've got the hottest (but never out of style) bracelet around. 

Each bracelet is 7" inches long with 1" of adjustable chain for comfort.

options.name: mixed chain - 14k gold fill & sterling silver bracelet

name: Julie hand-wrapped hoop earrings
description:
Jewelry crush. These are the ones. They stopped us in our tracks... Ever since we saw the Julie bracelet we were dying for the just as sexy earring version and FINALLY, they are here. 

Expertly hand-wrapped with gorgeous stones. And at 1" wide and 1.5" in length they are just as perfect for work as they are when out and about. 

Oh, and the moonstone version makes a stunning wedding earring...

name: Carrie earrings
description:
Long and graceful like our friend Carrie, these "I can do it all" earrings measure approx 2.25" long and just over .5" wide. 

We love them for many reasons, because they are SUPER lightweight, because we love organic shapes that move as we do and well, cause these ladies can work hard and play hard (yeah, we took it there...).

name: Hanna half moon necklace
description:
Get this!
It goes with EVERYTHING! Casual, dressy, whatever.
It's light, architectural, classic, understated and quite frankly, just darn perfect in its simplicity.

(plus, it's shaped like a horse shoe and that's super good luck)

It hangs 16.5" long with a 2.25" extender and has a beautiful hammered texture. Half moon shape is approximately 1" across.

name: Devorah long crystal necklace
description:
Pure enlightenment looks so good... 

One gorgeous chunky gemstone with an expertly wrapped clear quartz crystal on a 34" chain.

We love an easy to wear statement piece. This is it!

name: extra long "key to my heart" necklace
description:
It's the skeleton key necklace you have come to know and love - only on a thicker and longer chain. BUT WAIT, there's more. It's on 34" of cable chain but with a clasp...so if you want to wear it shorter you can clasp it wherever you want and then you have a long hot chain finished with a garnet drop hanging down. It's like a necklace with a free bonus necklace.

Due to the vintage nature of the keys, no two are the same. If you'd prefer to see pictures of your key before we send it off, just ask. Otherwise we will pick a wonderful one for you!

name: Lady luck horseshoe ring
description:
Maybe you or a friend need a little extra luck? Maybe you're already so lucky your friends call you Vegas? Maybe you have super fond memories of your first childhood pony ride? Whatever the case may be, this ring is awesome. Delicate, feminine and best of all, super lucky! 

One for you and one for your bestie.

*don't see your ring size listed? Just send us a note with the proper size and we'll take care  of it!

name: Daniella gift necklace
description:
As our friend Dana said, "this necklace is a little Valentine for your neck!" We agree. And really, who doesn't want to be a Valentine all year round? We think year round love is the way to go.

This sweet pea of a necklace is 16.5" long and centered with 3 little clusters of gift-wrapped gemstone goodness. Finished with our hand-made hammered ring.

Want it longer? Just ask...

name: Jessie Earrings
description:
We had an informal naming contest for these new stunners and here's what our friend Allison had to say about her mom Jessie:

"She was diagnosed with pancreatic cancer in January and has been a fighter ever since. Not only does she fight but she does it with class and charm. Your earrings remind me of her. Every part of her is a jewel, but mostly her golden, warm heart."

And so they have been named! And so you will be even more stunning with them on. We can't even believe how much we love them! 

Even better, 10% of the proceeds will go to The Lustgarten Foundation for pancreatic cancer research. Look good and feel good doing it!

name: Maya earrings
description:
Meet Maya...

A lovely hammered hoop earring with a gemstone hand-wrapped in the opposite metal. 1.5" long and just under 1" wide. Lightweight and easy to wear.

Pure goodness.

name: Stephanie Necklace
description:
The Stephanie necklace is sexy... not in a "in your face" way - rather, in a "I'm so cool it hurts" kind of a way. 

This necklace will take you there. Effortless bohemian chic.

14.5" of chain centered with a 2" hammered metal bar. Add a hand-wrapped, faceted gemstone in the opposite metal and viola, you're ready.

Oh, and end that bad boy with 2.5" of extender chain to give you length options and top it off with our hand made A (agapantha) charm.

name: Sandye swirl stud earrings
description:
Ya'll have been asking for a stud earring for years... and now, it's here and we're totally in love.

A hand-made swirl (about 1/3 of an inch in diameter) of sterling silver or 14k gold fill on our signature 1.25" long post. No pesky earring backing needed - you just put it in and pinch it down. The metal is slightly malleable so you can make little adjustments. That overhang of the post adds just enough of an edgy touch while still being tame enough for the office. 

You know how the easiest to wear and most simple in style is often the sexiest? Yeah, that.

name: Jaime long on time necklace
description:
We can't give you more hours in the day, but we can help you look good all day long... 

34" of chain centered with gorgeous vintage watch parts. Gears, faces, movements all uniquely combined to give you the perfect one of a kind necklace. 

Isn't it time you treated yourself?

name: Jaime tick tock earrings
description: Ever feel like there just aren't enough hours in the day? Get it all done while looking good with these tick tock vintage watch part earrings. A sterling silver or 14k gold filled hoop (approx 1.25" x .75") with an array of interesting watch parts expertly wrapped around the edges. Delicate and industrial and each pair is one of a kind.

name: Hanna hammered hoops
description:
Hanna hammered hoops... great alliteration, right? Also, GREAT gal and GREAT earrings.

Super lightweight with just the right amount of shiny hammered texture to give your everyday a little bling.

Large = 2.5" long x 1.75" wide
Medium = 1.75" long x 1.25" wide
Small = 1.5" long x 1" wide

name: Lila earrings
description: Lovely Lila... 3 beautiful gently twisted sterling silver or 14k gold fill hoops finished with a hand-wrapped gemstone. At approximately 2" long it's the perfect compliment to your work day - or your night out.

name: Trisha earring
description:
Feminine oval hoops with gracefully wrapped gemstone clusters. Flirty, fun and floral. Great for every day wear with eye catching, envy inspiring stone combinations.

1" wide x 1.5" long and lightweight!

name: Jaime vintage watch parts charm bracelet
description:
The delicate and industrial come together and form the perfect piece of repurposed jewelry. Over a dozen hand picked vintage watch parts hang charm style from a light cable chain that's finished with garnet.

You will wonder how you ever lived without it.

At 6.75" long with an inch+ extender, this will fit most wrists. Have a smaller wrist? No problem, you can clasp the bracelet anywhere to adjust the size.

name: Evanne earrings
description:
Stop.
Hammer(ed) time.

The Evanne hammered hoop earrings are 3" of sparkly, dangly goodness. Each earring has 5 half inch hammered hoops hanging organically from diamond cut chain. Oh yes!

Parachute pants are optional.

name: Natasha earring
description:
The Natasha earring is delicate and sexy without being an attention hog. Three hand-wrapped oval gemstones hang on shimmering diamond cut chain. At 1.75" long they are lightweight and perfect for all day - every day wear. 

Oh, and don't be afraid to consider them for a hot night out...they clean up nicely, just like you!

name: Sarah Dagger Hoops
description:
The Sarah Dagger hoop earring is one of our favorites... After all, who doesn't look great in a hoop? They look amazing with everything...appropriate for work, the weekends and just like you, they dress up nice. 

They hang just shy of 2" long and measure 1.25" wide.

Color options: onyx, amazonite and olive jade.

name: Laura single leaf necklace
description:
Our good friends Oprah and Hesta Prynn from Northern State both love this necklace... We're confident you'll feel the same.

One beautiful carved stone leaf on 17" of diamond cut chain with gemstone accents. It's Autumn all year round!

All Agapantha necklaces have a 2" extender so you can raise or lower your necklace to suit your outfit.

Available in olive jade and brown carnelian.

name: Beth triple hoop earrings
description: Red Carpet glamour! At approximately 2.5" long the Beth earrings sparkle and shine with faceted gemstones of varying shapes and sizes.  Wear your hair up and really show them off...pair them with jeans and a tank...knock 'em dead in your sexiest dress... no matter how you wear them the spotlight is yours. The hand-formed hoops have amazing movement and an organic feel that are at once seductive and grounded. Which means, you can feel beautiful in them any day - any time!

name: Sarah tiny cluster necklace
description:
This necklace screams of sweet, sweet warm weather and delicious breezes... It looks at us playfully and begs to be paired with a flowy dress and sandals. 

Is it possible that the necklace actually brings the gorgeous weather? If so, we're NEVER taking it off!

One tiny hoop (about the size of a dime) with a playfully dainty cluster of stones hangs from a 17" diamond cut chain. Of course, you have your 2" adjuster on the back if you'd like to wear it longer.

This is a great option for bridesmaids!

name: Andi vintage chandelier hoop earring
description:
These earrings appeared before us like a vision. A hand-formed hoop earring (approx 1.25" wide x 1.75" long) with one glorious piece of light refracting history from a vintage chandelier.

Get ready to make rainbows wherever you go.

name: Daniella gift earrings
description:
A cluster of 4 gemstones hand gift-wrapped with 14k gold fill or sterling silver wire. It's like a special present for your ears.

At about 1/2" long these are perfect for just about any setting (we like to wear them to the gym...we hate to have naked ears!) and they make a fantastic affordable gift.

name: Anais small charm necklace
description:
The charm necklace you've always wanted... The Anais charm necklace is a sexy combination of gemstones and charms on 16.5" of diamond cut chain. 

People will stop you on the street. We promise.

All Agapantha necklaces have a 2" extender so you can raise or lower your necklace to suit your outfit.

Available in: 
PURPLE & RED (quartz, amethyst, coral, pearl)

PINKS (jade, quartz, rhodonite, pearl)

GOLD SPARKLE & PLUM (goldstone, garnet, citrine, pearl)

CLEAR & WHITE (quartz, moonstone, jade, pearl)

YELLOW & NAVY (quartz, iolite, lapiz lazuli, citrine, pearl)

name: Nichole single stone necklace
description:
Layer it, wear it alone...no matter how you wear it, you will want one in every color. (we especially love this necklace when layered on top of the Vanessa triple chain necklace)

The Nichole single stone necklace is the answer to having a little something special hugging your neck. One glorious gemstone suspended on 16.5" of diamond cut chain, with our signature asymmetrical tiny gemstone triplet . And don't forget the 2" of adjustable chain (finished with another gemstone!) that allows you to lengthen or shorten your necklace to suit your neckline.

And brides - this is our #1 most popular bridesmaid gift. We can custom make these necklaces in pretty much any color you need!

name: Amy chain wrapped hoop earrings
description:
Hoops that shine and glitter and catch the light with every move you make... Subtle enough to wear all day and flashy enough to get you noticed! 

They hang just under 1.75" long and 1.25" wide

Because, you deserve to get noticed!

name: Sarah tiny drop earring
description:
We are so into the Sarah tiny drop earring we composed a haiku...

you are simple, sweet
one glorious gemstone falls
sarah, this is love

We love this earring. Love it, love it, love it. We have it in every color because it is light and simple and so super wearable while still making us look amazing. Enough said.

Approximately 1" long and about .33" wide.

Available in amethyst (light purple), garnet (deep plum), clear quartz (crystal clear), rose quartz (pale pink) and citrine (translucent yellow)  

Want to wear these for your wedding? We can do them in clear quartz, white topaz, mystic topaz, pearls...

name: Anais long necklace
description:
This stunning 34" necklace with one giant shimmering gemstone (1.5" x 1.25") slips easily over your head and is the perfect compliment to dresses, high neck sweaters, and t-shirts.  Ok, it looks great with everything... So slip it on!

Available in white quartz, goldstone and yellow quartz.

name: Vintage "key to my heart" Necklace
description:
Vintage skeleton keys are so mysterious and romantic. We decided to add 17" of diamond cut chain so we could wear these one-of-a-kind beauties around our necks...

We hand pick these keys at estate sales (and wherever we find ones we love) so no 2 are ever the same. Unique just like you!

Necklace is finished with garnets and a 2" extender for an adjustable fit. 

You are not buying the actual keys pictured so If you want to see a picture of the one we have chosen for you just ask. All keys pictured are between 2.5"-3" long.

name: Sarah tiny triple hoop necklace
description:
Did someone say perfect necklace? 

3 hand shaped oval hoops are the quintessential backdrop to a single shimmering gemstone. Add 17" of diamond cut chain and you have a gorgeous, but simple necklace.

All Agapantha necklaces have a 2" extender so you can raise or lower your necklace to suit your outfit.

This has also been a popular choice for brides! Want it in white topaz, mystic topaz or maybe a little blue topaz drop for your "something blue?" Just ask!

name: Emily necklace
description:
Oh so sweet and petite she is, our dear friend Emily. When you want a little something sparkly, but not overpowering, this is it! This is definitely our new classic!

16" chain with 2 + inch extender at the back with coordinated gemstone drop.

Available in more stones and colors than pictured. Want something you don't see? Just call or email us and we should be able to to do it for you. No problemo!

name: Rebekah small cluster hoop earrings
description:
Small hand-formed hoop earrings with a cluster of eye-catching gemstones dangling from the bottom. At just over 1" long you get the perfect understated punch of color.

We love to wear them to yoga and we're not embarrassed to admit it.

Available in white pearl, copper, garnet, red coral and amazonite.

name: Julie bangle bracelet
description:
Slip into our sexiest bracelet. A hand-formed bangle wrapped with wire and covered with gorgeous gemstones. Each stone is expertly hand-wrapped and one-size-fits-most. If you are concerned about the size or know you'll need a bigger one, just ask and we'll custom make it for you.

One looks beautiful...stack 2 or 3 and WOW!

We are especially excited to announce the addition of our moonstone wedding edition finished with one single iolite (dusty blue!) stone for good bride karma.

name: Rebekah cascade earrings
description:
There are so many reasons why these might be the best earrings ever...

1. They weigh nothing. You don't even realize you're wearing earrings.
2. Beautiful organic shapes.
3. They move and flow with you in the sexiest way. Seriously.
4. They manage to move between casual and dressy without effort.

You might actually NEED these.

These fine earrings hang approximately 2.25" long.

name: Melissa necklace
description:
Our new Melissa necklace is sugar AND spice and most things nice(ish). We take a delicate piece of sterling silver chain and center it with an industrial gold tone vintage chain for a perfect combination of good girls gone just a little bit bad. Add a few tiny rough cut garnets and let the games begin.

16" chain with 2 + inch extender at the back with a garnet drop.

name: Osmara dagger earring
description:
Just like our friend Osmara, these earrings have understated sass. Subdued enough for the office, but with enough color and pizazz  to wear any old time. 

At 1.5" long we bet your mom will like these as much as you do. Our mom can't keep her hands off... 

Available in honey jade, amazonite, hot pink jade, cherry quartz and laborodite.

name: Nichole large single stone necklace
description:
Sometimes bigger is better... If you love the Nichole single stone necklace, but you want a little more  bling,  this is your necklace! Layer it, wear it alone, double them up. However you do it, this will be your new everyday necklace!

The Nichole Lg single stone necklace is the perfect accessory. One glorious gemstone suspended on 17" of diamond cut chain. And don't forget the 2" of adjustable chain (finished with another gemstone!) that allows you to lengthen or shorten your necklace to suit your outfit.

Available in: white quartz, amethyst, hot pink jade and yellow quartz.

name: Beth triple hoop necklace
description:
A statement necklace, you ask? This stunner showcases 3 hand-formed oval hoops in descending sizes with one glorious plum colored garnet dangling from the center of each. We love the organic shapes and the movement of this piece.

Oh so modern.

The diamond cut chain is 16.5" long and the hoops hang approximately 4.5" long from the center. As always, there is a 2" adjustable extender chain at back finished this time with a beautiful garnet drop.

name: Piri cocktail earring
description:
Take one part vintage chandelier, one part semi-precious gemstone and add one part flirty fun. The Piri cocktail earring is the perfect match for that wedding you have next month and doubles as total hotness with jeans and a tank.

Measures approximately 1.5" to 1.75"

name: Large Sarah Hoop earrings
description:
The Sarah Hoop.

No bells and whistles here. A perfect plain hoop earring. Again, say your mantra... "HOOP EARRINGS LOOK HOT ON EVERYONE!"

Hand formed oval shaped hoops. Super duper lightweight and approximately 1.75" long x 1.25" wide.

name: Lg Sarah chain hoops
description:
(W)Hoop it up in the large Sarah chain hoops with a single dangling stone...

Each hand-formed hoop is made with love and with the sparkly drop hangs about 2.5" long and 1.75" wide. As always, they are lightweight and super comfortable. 

Just like our friend Sarah, these earrings have attitude. So be prepared to back that up or wear them when you need a little extra!

Available in electric blue jade, dark green jade, amethyst (light purple) and cherry quartz (salmon pink).

name: Daniella long cluster earring
description:
Our friend Daniella is super playful and undeniably sexy. We designed these earrings for her and feel confident that they are right on the mark.

2" of layered chain cascades down from our signature "gift-wrapped" cluster of gemstones. (hangs 2.5" total)

Available in: amazonite, copper and smoky quartz.

name: Daniella earring
description:
Daniella earrings are like a little gift for your ears. One teardrop shaped stone dangles playfully from a cluster of "gift-wrapped" stones.

At just over 1" long these are great for everyday and make fantastic gifts!

name: Amethyst Chip Ring
description:
The amethyst chip ring!

Who doesn't want to wear a ring that not only looks fantastic but also promotes peace, calm, balance and courage? What a great gift for a friend or loved one...or yourself!

All of our hand-crafted chip rings are made with gorgeous gemstone pieces and no two are ever the same! Equally as stunning in sterling silver or 14k gold-fill and available in half-sizes. 

Need a size you don't see? Just email us and ask...we'll make it for you no problem.

name: Quinn necklace
description:
Our friend Quinn is bold, outspoken and simply beautiful. If that's you (or how you'd like to feel!) then this is your necklace.

One gorgeous gemstone (approx 1.25" long and 1" wide) floats on 17" of stunning cable chain. And of course, there's the 2" extender at the back so you can raise and lower the necklace as necessary.

Available in: olive jade and cherry quartz

name: Ronit earrings
description:
Red carpet anyone? A cascade of faceted gemstones sparkling from every direction definitely demand attention. Get ready for the paparazzi!

Rich colors and beautiful rope chain at just about 2" long. These ARE your holiday season accessory - and well, also your anytime accessory too.

name: Mary wrapped hoop earrings
description:
Sometimes it's all about the details. We love pearls, but aren't really feeling a traditional pearl earring. We want a pop of color with an easy hoop earring. 

Timeless and timely, just like our friend Mary.

These little treasures measure approximately 1.5" long and 1" wide.

And if we may recommend, these are great for brides and bridal parties...

Available in white pearl, turquoise and red coral. (ask about custom colors!)

name: Green Aventurine Chip Ring
description:
Your friends will be green with envy when you're wearing the chip ring in aventurine!

Know anyone that needs a little extra help in the prosperity and career success department? They say green aventurine is the gemstone for the job! Already madly successful? Well then keep it going and look good in the process.

All of our hand-crafted chip rings are made with gorgeous gemstone pieces and no two are ever the same! Equally as stunning in sterling silver or 14k gold-fill and available in half-sizes. 

Need a size you don't see? Just email us and ask...we'll make it for you no problem.

name: Rebekah medium hoop earring
description:
Ok, we have to admit something... At one point we wore our Rebekah med hoops for like 4 months straight without ever deviating. That's how much we love them. There's more of a healthy rotation going now, but these bad boys really make us feel hot, hot, hot whenever we slip them on.

They measure 1.25" long and 1" wide. For the love of hoops, get yourself (and your BFF) a pair of these pronto. 

Available in blue & pink (jade, chalcedony, stardust), green (jade, aventurine, amazonite, turquoise), purple & red (amethyst & coral), orange & yellow (citrine, carnelian, pearl).

name: Daniella dagger earring
description:
Daniella earrings are like a little gift for your ears. Add the long marquis shaped stone to the cluster of "gift-wrapped" stones and you have sexy playfulness.

At just over 1.5" long these are great for everyday and have just enough bite to really spice up the evening!

Available in: garnet & honey jade, turquoise & lilac quartz and lapiz and honey jade.

name: Med Sarah chain hoop
description:
The perfect size hoop earring for all the ladies. Aw yeah. 

Each hand-formed hoop is made with love and with the sparkly drop hangs just shy of 2" long and 1" wide. As always, they are lightweight and super comfortable.

Just like our friend Sarah, these earrings have attitude. So be prepared to back that up or wear them when you need a little extra!

Available in electric blue jade, dark green jade, amethyst (light purple) and citrine (translucent yellow).

name: Eliza earring
description:
Eliza loves her jewels long and sparkly. We are so with her on that...

We're talking 2.75" of assorted layered chains and sparkling gemstones in various shapes and sizes. Feminine, flirty and fierce. We especially love to mix it up and wear these with jeans and a t-shirt just to keep 'em guessing.

name: Gillian chandelier earrings
description:
When we wear the Gillian chandelier earrings we feel beautiful. Twirling through a field of dandelions beautiful.

The perfect touch of femininity, we love to wear these earrings when getting all dolled up...but there's something about wearing them with skinny jeans, boots and a t-shirt. The balance. Totally beautiful.

Just shy of 2.5" and extremely lightweight.

name: Daniella earring in white topaz
description:
We can't get over the sheer elegance of the marquis cut white topaz in this special wedding version of the Daniella earring.

And no, it doesn't mean you have to be a bride to wear this earring. It just means this earring is gorgeous enough to wear on your most magical of days. We like to wear them with jeans and a t-shirt sometimes...and daydream away.

This earring measures just over 1" long and looks incredible in sterling silver and gold!

name: Black and white candy ring
description:
This ring bestows it's wearer with energy and integrity - just some of the qualities of onyx and pearl. And even if it didn't, the cluster of black and white gemstones is a real knockout. 

Need a size you don't see offered? Just email us and we'll make it happen!

name: Sarah small hoops with chain cascade
description:
Somehow this tiny earring manages to be completely alarmingly hot...while being totally understated. The combination of the hand-formed oval hoop and waterfall of sparkly diamond cut chain is just electric.

At only 1.25" long and so light you won't even remember you are wearing jewelry, these are a great alternative to studs. Perfect for dressing up an outfit and small and simple enough for every day wear.

name: Becca twisted hoop earrings
description:
A "twist" on the regular hoop earring... A hand-twisted hoop with a single teardrop shaped stone. At approx 1.5" long and .75" wide it's lightweight, easy to wear and makes a fabulous gift!

Available in: hot pink jade, electric blue jade and amethyst.

name: Correne triangle earrings
description:
We love the Correne triangle earrings for invoking both the 1980's and the future - in one fell swoop. They have great movement and at just over 2" long, they are dangly without being too long for the timid.

Available in: leopard jasper, peach jade, kiwi jade and onyx.

name: Robyn Earring
description:
The Robyn earring is a glorious tear drop shape delicately hanging from the bottom of layered curb chain. Lightweight and 2.5" long, these earrings looks great on everyone and are ideal for everyday wear. (these make a great gift for those of you overwhelmed by choices!)

Available in cream mother of pearl, white mother of pearl, pink mother of pearl and abalone.

name: Vintage knitting needle bangle bracelet
description:
Do you love to Knit? Do you have a friend that does? Do you love this bracelet as much as we do and don't care that you have no idea how to knit?

The colors are amazing and we love that they are vintage. And because they are, no one bracelet is ever exactly the same. Hand-formed and ready to slip on your wrist. 

Oh, and they are a great conversation piece. Get talking!

All bangles are one size fits all! If you'd like to see a pic of the exact one we're choosing for you before purchasing, just email us and ask!

name: Vintage Vodka Liquor Tag Necklace
description:
You love a stiff drink! Wear your poison around your neck...let the bartender know what you'd like, let the cute guy at the bar buy you a drink, let the world know!

All of our liquor tags are vintage and found at estate sales...oh the stories they could tell! Now go out and make your own and feel good knowing you will be wearing a one-of-a-kind piece of re-worked vintage jewelry.

This necklace measures between 17" and 19.25" depending on where you'd like it to rest.

Cheers!

***Back in the day, it was customary to fill a crystal decanter with your booze of choice instead of keeping it in the bottle. A decanter tag was used to "label" the bottle in style. Now you can label yourself in style...

name: Vintage Brass Rye Liquor Tag Necklace
description:
Oh sweet Gin, how I love you so...

Let everyone know just how you feel with this one-of-a-kind necklace made with a combination of vintage and new chains and gorgeous metal and enamel vintage liquor tag. The tag is stamped made in England and regardless of where you're from we bet people will offer to buy you a drink!

With just over 17" of adjustable mixed chains around your neck, you will feel like the life of the party.

As with all of our vintage pieces, no 2 are ever the same. So, if Gin is your drink...now is the time to shout it to the world.

Don't see your favorite poison? Email us and if we have it, we will custom make it for you!

options.name: Vintage Brass Rye Liquor Tag Necklace

name: Piri mixed chain earrings
description:
Vintage glamour abounds with the Piri chain earrings.

Each earring features a light catching vintage chandelier piece and 5 strands of perfectly mismatched vintage chains. These shimmering beauties measure approximately 3" long.

This is one of those perfect accessories - great with jeans and a t-shirt and more than appropriate for a night to remember...

name: Vintage Bourbon Liquor Tag Necklace
description:
Wear it proud! You love Bourbon and you're not afraid to shout it out. A gorgeous vintage gold-tone chain finished with garnets and 14k gold fill chain frame the centerpiece - a classic vintage liquor tag (2.5" long x 1.25" wide) - that reads BOURBON! 

As with all of our vintage pieces, no two are ever the same. So don't hesitate cause this my friend, is one of a kind!

***Back in the day, it was customary to fill a crystal decanter with your booze of choice instead of keeping it in the bottle. A decanter tag was used to "label" the bottle in style. Now you can label yourself in style...

Don't see your favorite poison? Email us and if we have it, we will custom make it for you!

name: Kelli necklace
description:
The Kelli necklace is super classic, versatile and (meow) sexy. Let all 44" hang down over your favorite dress or top - or double it up for a great layered look.

Available in white pearl.
(ask about other colors...we can make them no problem!)

name: Nichole single stone necklace in white topaz
description:
The Nichole single stone necklace is the answer to having a little something special hugging your neck. One sparkling white topaz suspended on 17" of diamond cut chain. And don't forget the 2" of adjustable chain (finished with white pearls!) that allows you to lengthen or shorten your necklace to suit your outfit.

We love this necklace for brides... so simple and elegant. We have word that most of our brides wear this necklace constantly even after they say I do.

name: Rachel long knotted earring
description:
If you want to stop the show, these are the earrings for you. At just shy of 4" long the Rachel earring is a knotted cascade of dazzling diamond cut chain with 3 rough cut tear drop shaped gemstones.

And don't think you have to be 7 feet tall to pull these off... Just be ready to stun.

Available in: amethyst with lilac pearl and citrine with garnet

name: Rebekah large hoop earrings
description:
Every single time we step out in these hoops we get compliments... who doesn't love compliments?

These are the deluxe version of the Rebekah medium hoops and we think they make us look positively bad ass.

Approximately 2" long x 1.75" wide... Word!

name: Daniella tiered drop earrings
description:
If the regular Daniella earrings are little gifts for your ears, then these are a shopping spree!

Designed with a very special wedding in mind - we decided we can't even wait for the big day to put these on. So feminine, so easy and so beautiful. Perfect for dressing up, surprisingly fabulous when dressing down.

They measure 2.25" and hang from a simple earwire.

For a wedding? We can do custom colors, just ask!

sterling silver - white pearl & clear quartz

name: Vanessa 5 chain necklace
description:
The Vanessa 5 chain necklace is one of the first pieces ever designed for Agapantha and is our best seller to this day... Why you ask? We truly believe there is nothing more classic and sexy than a cascade of layered chains hanging from your neck. 5 chains in varying shapes and sizes (though all delicate and lightweight) will never go out of style and very easily translates from day into evening. Layer your favorite pendant necklace over the top, wear it with a low cut dress to a gala, have a few chains poking out under your collared shirt - no matter how you wear it, it looks great and feels even better against your skin. 5 chains too much for you? Try the Vanessa 3 chain for a more subtle layered look!

The chains start at 16" and go to approx 24" with a 2" extender on the back of the necklace.

name: Vanessa mixed 6 chain necklace
description:
Want to wear all of your gold, silver and platinum jewelry at once? 

The Vanessa 6 chain necklace is one of the first pieces ever designed for Agapantha and is our best seller to this day... Why you ask? We truly believe there is nothing more classic and sexy than a cascade of layered chains hanging from your neck. 6 chains in varying shapes and sizes (though all delicate and lightweight) will never go out of style and very easily translates from day into evening. Layer your favorite pendant necklace over the top, wear it with a low cut dress to a gala, have a few chains poking out under your collared shirt - no matter how you wear it, it looks great and feels even better against your skin. 6 chains too much for you? Try the Vanessa 3 chain for a more subtle layered look!

The chains start at 16" and go to approx 24" with a 2" extender on the back of the necklace.

name: Daniella wedding necklace
description:
Delicate, dainty, flirty and ultra feminine, wear it and feel like a princess. Though we definitely support the wearing of this fine necklace with any old outfit, it was designed especially for the most special of days...your wedding! The combination of hand wrapped pearls and topaz will give you that heirloom look and why not incorporate the pale blue/silvery pearls for your "something blue?" So subtle and so lovely.

Necklace measures 16" for a close fit and includes a 2" extender at back if you want to wear it a little lower. Finished with a gorgeous white topaz that will hang at the back of your neck. Great if you will be wearing your hair up!

As always, we love to do weddings. Do you need other colors? Just ask...we can make it happen!

name: Millie stick pearl earring
description:
The Millie stick pearl earrings are a modern take on a classic style. The beautiful shimmery stick pearl with a beautiful teardrop stone on the bottom. Simple, elegant and so easy to wear.

Length varies by pearl length, but they are between 1.5 and 1.75" long.

name: Ali drape earring
description:
Oh the sexy, sexy Ali earring! If you're a fan of the double take (especially when walking down the aisle), these glorious draped wonders have your name all over them. They hang approximately 2.25" long.

They hang 2.25" long and can be custom made in other colors!

sterling silver - white pearl & clear quartz

name: Diana necklace
description:
Can you be both bold and delicate? We say yes! We love the strong geometric design and flow of this necklace. So clean, simple and modern...and still so feminine. Easy to wear every day and the perfect accessory for an evening out. We say hallelujah! 

Necklace measures approx 17" long with 2 + inch extender in the back.

name: Diana lg. mixed metal earrings
description:
We love to throw caution to the wind and wear all of our gold and silver jewelry together. These earrings were created with that rebellious spirit in mind... A large oval hoop in one metal with the smaller oval shapes in the opposite. They have fantastic movement and are so unique and modern. We can't get enough.

These beauties are approximately 2.5" long.

options.name: Lg 14k gold hoop w/ sterling silver drops
Lg sterling silver hoop w/ 14k gold fill drops

name: Diana med earrings
description:
New favorite alert! 

Dear Diana earrings, 
Where have you been all my life? Your strong - yet feminine shapes, the way you move when I move... I think I am in love.

Just trust us here... you will love these and none of your friends will have them (until they see yours that is)! 

Approximately 2-2.25" long.

name: Jaime vintage watch parts charm necklace
description:
Delicate, meet Industrial... A match made in vintage heaven.

7 different vintage watch parts hang charm-like from a 16.5" diamond cut chain. Want it a little longer? You have another 2+ inches from the extender...also finished with a cool piece of time making history.

Don't you think it's "TIME" to get one of these bad boys for yourself? (get it, time?)

name: Jaime tiny hoop earrings
description: Tiny little hoops (about the size of a dime) adorned with a handful of perfectly mismatched vintage watch parts. So small and light that they are great for the office and everyday wear. And once people notice what they are - you get extra points in the coolness dept.

name: Jaime small hoop earrings
description:
If you love your hoops, but you're jonesing for a little something extra these earrings have got your number...

A small oval hoop (approx 1" long x 3/4" wide) with a handful of mismatched vintage watch parts dangling from the center. 

There will be oohs and aahs. We've seen it.

name: tiny Jaime dangle earring
description:
Oh the marriage of delicate jewelry and unexpected industrial timepieces. 

One tiny oval hoop (about the size of a dime) with an assortment of thoughtfully mismatched vintage watch parts dangles from 1" of chain.

Super interesting, very lightweight and we think, a match made in heaven.

name: Vintage Gin Decanter tag necklace
description:
Gin, Gin, Gin...

Let everyone know just how you feel with this one-of-a-kind necklace made with a combination of vintage chains and a fancy Italian made vintage liquor tag.

With just over 17" of mixed chain (with 3+ inches of extra adjustable chain to make it longer or shorter) around your neck, you're ready for some serious Gin and Tonic time.

As with all of our vintage pieces, no 2 are ever the same. So, if Gin is your drink...now is the time to shout it to the world.

***Back in the day, it was customary to fill a crystal decanter with your booze of choice instead of keeping it in the bottle. A decanter tag was used to "label" the bottle in style. Now you can label yourself in style...

Don't see your favorite poison? Email us and if we have it, we will custom make it for you! 

These beauties make a great gift!

name: Jennifer earrings
description:
Hand-formed oval hoops with organically wrapped gemstones - like a delicately cultivated sparkly garden for your ears.

Jennifer oh Jenny.

Approximately 1.75" long.

name: Jaime stripped down time necklace
description:
Whether you have the time or not, this is the necklace... Complicated, delicate, interesting, fun and a real conversation piece, just like you!

16.5" of diamond cut chain with one deconstructed vintage time piece, one watch face and one sparkly gemstone. Finished with a 2" chain extender and vintage watch part piece.

All necklaces are one of a kind! 

Want another color stone? Just ask!

name: Jaime triple threat necklace
description:
3 amazing deconstructed vintage watch pieces make for a fascinating and darkly feminine centerpiece. On 16" of diamond cut chain with a 2" extender so you can wear it as high or low as you'd like. Finished with faceted garnets.

No two pieces are ever exactly the same...and we think you'll like it that way!

name: Jaime one-of-a-kind necklace
description:
We don't want anyone to get in a fight, but there's only ONE of these necklaces...

One gorgeous vintage pocket watch component with beautiful etchings and engraved W.P.Sedgwick on 16" of diamond cut sterling silver chain with a 2" extender.

Plain and simple, this necklace is bad ass. And, once it's yours - no one else will ever own it. (insert evil laugh)

name: Max mixed chain necklace
description: 34"of mismatched vintage chain. Tones of gold, silver, brass and copper in different textures and weights - connected with tiny faceted garnets or jump rings for a unisex vibe.  Wear it alone - layer it.

options.name: Max mixed chain necklace with garnet
Max mixed chain necklace with jump rings

name: Gift Certificate
description:
Can't decide what gorgeous piece of jewelry to give? You don't have to! Give an Agapantha gift certificate and let the shopping begin... We will email or mail the certificate at no cost.

Need a different denomination? Just email us at info@agapantha.com and ask. It's no problem!

name: Ronit earrings in white topaz marquis
description:
Hands down our most sophisticated stunners! A cascade of faceted marquis shaped white topaz sparkling from every direction absolutely demands attention.

These beauties hang just about 2" long making them a perfect accompaniment to your wedding dress, red carpet gown, or cocktail attire. (and as always - pair them with boyfriend jeans and a tank...)

Wearing these for your wedding and want to incorporate a little something blue? We can top them with a subtle light blue pearl or a dusty iolite. Need a picture of these examples? Just ask!

name: Mary wrapped hoops with drop
description:
Sometimes it's all about the details. We love pearls, but aren't really feeling a traditional pearl earring. Instead, we love this hand-formed oval hoop wrapped with pearls and centered with a delicate, faceted briolet gemstone for extra sparkle and shine. These are one of most popular choices for brides and bridal parties!

Timeless and timely, just like our friend Mary.

These little treasures measure approximately 1.5" long and 1" wide.

Available in a wide range of colors (just ask about custom colors and stones!)

name: Vanessa charm bracelet
description:
Effortless, classic, and undeniably sexy, the Vanessa charm bracelet is 5 strands of alternating 14k gold fill (and/or) sterling silver chain in all different styles, shapes and textures with a hand-picked selection of gorgeous gemstones and pearls. Finish each end with rough cut stones and a shimmering briolet drop that hangs seductively off the wrist and you've got the most stunning bracelet around. We love this as a wedding bracelet!

Each bracelet is 7" inches long with 1" of adjustable chain for comfort.

Is this for your wedding? Want us to add a little something blue? It's no problem!

name: Becca twisted hoops with white topaz marquis
description:
A "twist" on the standard hoop earring...

A hand-twisted hoop with a single faceted marquis shaped white topaz. At approx 1.5" long and .75" wide it's a lightweight, easy to wear stunner that we love for brides!

Want it bigger or smaller? We love custom orders...just ask!
